[?2004l[?2004h> In this task, you'"'"'ll build a Python script that uses RAG techniques to extract information from text documents and automatically fill in a PDF form. The script should map document content to form fields intelligently.
[?2004l[?2004h> 
[?2004l[?2004h> ## Resources
[?2004l[?2004h> The task includes pre-supplied files:
